Subject: [PATCH 5.4 13/57] ftrace: Move RCU is watching check after recursion check
Date:   Mon,  5 Oct 2020 17:26:25 +0200
Message-Id: <20201005142110.435571437@linuxfoundation.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.28.0
